title: Mythicmobs报错
author: 月见嘤嘤樱
txt_content:
[Craft Scheduler Thread - 952/WARN]: [MythicMobs] Plugin MythicMobs v4.7.2-FREE generated an exception while executing task 176
这是什么意思

replies.author: Dirito
replies.txt_content:
C_end 发表于 2020-2-24 13:08
Mobs里的那个DespawnByDefault吗？
是config里的“DespawnByDefault”

replies.author: Dirito
replies.txt_content:
解释非常复杂
设置config里的despawn选项为false即可
报错会消失
